## Desktop App Deployment

### Build Process

**Platforms Supported**:
- macOS: .dmg, .app
- Windows: .msi, .exe
- Linux: .deb, .AppImage

**Build Command**:
```bash
{{packageManager}} run tauri build
```

**Output Locations**:
```
src-tauri/target/release/bundle/
├── dmg/           # macOS installer
├── macos/         # macOS app bundle
├── msi/           # Windows installer
├── nsis/          # Windows installer (alternative)
├── deb/           # Debian/Ubuntu package
└── appimage/      # Universal Linux binary
```

### Code Signing

**macOS**:
```bash
# Sign app
codesign --deep --force --verify --verbose \
  --sign "Developer ID Application: Your Name" \
  "MyApp.app"

# Notarize
xcrun notarytool submit "MyApp.dmg" \
  --apple-id "your@email.com" \
  --password "app-specific-password" \
  --team-id "TEAM_ID"
```

**Windows**:
```powershell
# Sign with certificate
signtool sign /f certificate.pfx /p password /tr http://timestamp.digicert.com MyApp.exe
```

### Distribution

**GitHub Releases** (Recommended):
```bash
# Create release
gh release create v1.0.0 \
  src-tauri/target/release/bundle/dmg/*.dmg \
  src-tauri/target/release/bundle/msi/*.msi \
  src-tauri/target/release/bundle/deb/*.deb \
  src-tauri/target/release/bundle/appimage/*.AppImage
```

**Auto-Update Configuration**:
```json
// tauri.conf.json
{
  "tauri": {
    "updater": {
      "active": true,
      "endpoints": [
        "https://github.com/{{organization}}/{{projectName}}/releases/latest/download/latest.json"
      ],
      "dialog": true,
      "pubkey": "YOUR_PUBLIC_KEY_HERE"
    }
  }
}
```

### CI/CD Pipeline

```yaml
# .github/workflows/release.yml
name: Release Desktop App

on:
  push:
    tags:
      - 'v*'

jobs:
  release:
    strategy:
      matrix:
        platform: [macos-latest, windows-latest, ubuntu-latest]

    runs-on: ${{ matrix.platform }}

    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3

      - name: Setup Node.js
        uses: actions/setup-node@v3
        with:
          node-version: {{nodeVersion}}

      - name: Install Rust
        uses: actions-rs/toolchain@v1
        with:
          toolchain: stable

      - name: Install dependencies
        run: {{packageManager}} install

      - name: Build app
        run: {{packageManager}} run tauri build

      - name: Upload artifacts
        uses: actions/upload-artifact@v3
        with:
          name: ${{ matrix.platform }}-build
          path: src-tauri/target/release/bundle/

      - name: Create release
        uses: softprops/action-gh-release@v1
        with:
          files: src-tauri/target/release/bundle/**/*
```
