## Hybrid Deployment

### Desktop Client

See "Desktop App Deployment" section above.

### Cloud Backend

See "Web App Deployment" section above.

### Synchronization

**Update desktop app with backend URL**:
```bash
# .env.production (desktop app)
VITE_API_URL=https://api.production.example.com

# Rebuild desktop app with production API
{{packageManager}} run tauri build
```

**Deploy sequence**:
1. Deploy cloud backend first
2. Test backend endpoints
3. Update desktop app config with backend URL
4. Build desktop app
5. Release desktop app

**Version Compatibility**:
- Desktop app v1.x.x compatible with API v1.x.x
- Breaking changes require major version bump
- Auto-updater notifies users of new versions
